    <section id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                    <h2 style="font-size: 3em;">About</h2>
                    <p class="lead">
                        Watch With Me allows users to concurrently watch a video and chat live.<br><br>

                        Problem Scenario: Billy and Mandy want to watch a video together but are not in the same physical location. They load up a  video individually and attempt to start the video at the same time, but it is never truly synced. Billy needs to answer the door and leaves for a moment pausing his own video, but Mandy does not pause her video causing the videos to de-sync.<br><br>
                        
                        
                        Usage Scenario: Billy hops on Watch With Me and enters the video url. It generates a room where both Billy and Mandy can watch together!

                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <div class="modal fade" id="createModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
